## Transform Gizmo Actions

Each gizmo gives you access to different transform actions. By aiming the controllers at the manipulators highlighted below (usually on a translation, rotation, or scale gizmo for clarity), you can manipulate your Actor's Location, Rotation, and Scale independently.

| Action | Manipulator | Usage |
| --- | --- | --- |
|[REGION:none](#translate)[/REGION] **Translate** | ![](TranslateBar.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at one of the translation manipulators and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to move the selected Actor(s) along the axis. |
| [REGION:none](#translateplane)[/REGION]**Translate Plane** | ![](TranslatePlaneHighlight.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at one of the translation plane manipulators and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to move the selected Actor(s) along the plane (in 2 axes). |
|[REGION:none](#rotate)[/REGION] **Rotate** | ![](RotateHighlight.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at one of the rotation manipulators and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to rotate the selected Actor(s) around the axis. |
| [REGION:none](#uniformscale)[/REGION]**Uniform Scale** | ![](UniformScaleCube.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at the white cube in the center of the gizmo and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to scale the selected Actor(s) along all axes uniformly. |
| [REGION:none](#scale)[/REGION]**Scale** | ![](ScaleCube.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at one of the scale manipulator cubes and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to scale the selected Actor(s) along the selected axis. |
| [REGION:none](#scaleplane)[/REGION]**Scale Plane** | ![](ScalePlane.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at one of the scale manipulator planes and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to scale the selected Actor(s) along the selected plane. |
| [REGION:none](#stretch)[/REGION]**Stretch** |![](StretchHandles.png)(w:300) | Aim the controller at one of the stretch manipulators and squeeze the **Trigger** halfway to grab it. Move the controller to scale the selected Actor(s) non-uniformly along all axes while remaining anchored to the opposite corner.| 



  
